## ğŸ” Auth Routes (User Registration & Login)

### POST `/api/auth/register`
- Register a new user (username, email, password)

### POST `/api/auth/login`
- Log in and return JWT token

### GET `/api/auth/me`
- Get current logged-in user info (based on token)

---

## ğŸ‘¤ User Routes

### GET `/api/users/`
- Get all users (admin only)

### GET `/api/users/:id`
- Get user by ID

### PUT `/api/users/:id`
- Update user profile (name, email, etc.)

### DELETE `/api/users/:id`
- Delete a user (admin only)

---

## ğŸ“ Project Routes

### GET `/api/projects/`
- Get all projects for logged-in user

### POST `/api/projects/`
- Create new project

### GET `/api/projects/:id`
- Get specific project

### PUT `/api/projects/:id`
- Update project name, description, deadline

### DELETE `/api/projects/:id`
- Delete project and related tasks

---

## âœ… Task Routes

### GET `/api/tasks/`
- Get all tasks for user (optional filter: project, status, priority)

### POST `/api/tasks/`
- Create new task (title, description, deadline, projectId)

### GET `/api/tasks/:id`
- Get a single task

### PUT `/api/tasks/:id`
- Update task details (title, description, status)

### PATCH `/api/tasks/:id/complete`
- Mark task as complete/incomplete

### DELETE `/api/tasks/:id`
- Delete a task

---

## ğŸ’¬ Comment Routes (Optional)

### POST `/api/tasks/:taskId/comments`
- Add a comment to a task

### GET `/api/tasks/:taskId/comments`
- Get all comments for a task

